description: Plug in far away from home. This adapter connects an ungrounded 2-prong appliance to an outlet so you can keep your travel essentials powered. (Note that this adapter is not a voltage converter. Your device must be compatible with the voltage of the outlet you’re using.)Includes 2 adapter plugs.Suitable for use with 4mm round 2-pin plugs found in Europe.Accepts non-grounded plugs only (not 3-prong).
name: Sea To Summit Travel Adaptors - Europe
